customrecordtype.description: NextService Maintenance Record. Used to record details of maintenance/service of an Asset.

customrecordcustomfield.help: Field linking Asset to Maintenance record. Must be connected to NextService Asset field after bundling record to customer account. Set Record as Parent!
customrecordcustomfield.label: Asset

customrecordcustomfield.help: Case the maintenance record relates to. Used in config to capture details of repair on a case for an asset. Generally set via config rather than sourcing from Task.
customrecordcustomfield.label: Case

customrecordcustomfield.help: Task the maintenance record relates to. Note that filtering of this record is generally against the case rather than the asset, so the task will probably only be used to identify the task the record was created on, but the same maintenance record will be shown across all tasks related to this specific asset on this case.
customrecordcustomfield.label: Task

customrecordcustomfield.help: Project the maintenance is related to (via the Task). Generally set via config rather than sourcing from Task or Case.
customrecordcustomfield.label: Project

customrecordcustomfield.help: Field linking Parent Asset to Maintenance record. Must be connected to NextService Asset field after bundling record to customer account.
customrecordcustomfield.label: Parent Asset
